channel.title: Where to get laugh tracks
channel.description:
I need an assortment of laugh tracks for a project I'm working on, I've searched forums and torrent sites but I can't really find any decent files.
the only thing I can find is low quality audio that sounds like it was taken out of a cartoon. I'm looking for studio quality recordings(I know it's a lot to expect but surely someone has some?)
Does anyone know of a specialist forum or anywhere I could find things like this for private use? :)
